# CODEOWNERS — auto-requests review when PRs are opened to the default branch.
# Reference: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositories-settings-and-customizations/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# Format: <path-pattern>    <reviewer1> <reviewer2>

# Default owner — reviews any PR not matched by a more specific rule below.
*    @OWNER-GITHUB-USERNAME

# Optional: split ownership by folder for larger repos.
# /src/      @OWNER-GITHUB-USERNAME @CONTRIBUTOR-GITHUB-USERNAME
# /docs/     @OWNER-GITHUB-USERNAME
